description: Wake up to breathtaking sunrise views over Boston Harbor from this stunning corner residence in the heart of Seaport. With soaring 9'10" ceilings and floor-to-ceiling windows, this expansive 2Bed+, 2.5-bath home is bathed in natural light. The gourmet kitchen features Italian cabinetry, Wolf/Sub-Zero appliances, gas cooking, a wine fridge, and a marble waterfall island—perfect for entertaining. The serene primary bath offers a true spa experience with a steam shower, rainhead feature, and heated floors. Thoughtful details include custom handcrafted hardware, Sherle Wagner fixtures, and Phillip Jeffries wall coverings. Enjoy resort-style amenities: indoor pool, hot tub, steam room, sauna, treatment room, fitness center, and sports simulator. Residents also have access to a grand ocean view lounge with kitchen, private meeting room, hospitality suites, and priority seating at SAVR. Includes two garage parking spaces. Full-service building with concierge, valet, & door attendant.
